#: tutorial/controlflow.rst:986
msgid "Documentation Strings"
msgstr "Συμβολοσειρές Τεκμηρίωσης"

#: tutorial/controlflow.rst:993
msgid ""
"Here are some conventions about the content and formatting of documentation "
